Package: scupa
Title: Single-cell Unified Polarization analysis
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Wendao", "Liu", , "wendao.liu@uth.tmc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5124-9338"))
Description: This package provides trained machine learning models and methods to
    assess immune cell polarization. The models use Universial Cell Embeddings 
    (https://github.com/snap-stanford/UCE) to derive polarization scores and 
    statistically valid conformation predictions of polarization states defined 
    in Immune Dictionary (Cui et al. Nature. 2024).
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: Seurat (>= 4.0.0), Matrix, e1071
Suggests: randomForest, strip
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
NeedsCompilation: no
Author: Wendao Liu [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5124-9338>)
